com.xilinx.rapidwright.router

Class VersalClockTree

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.router.VersalClockTree

  • public class VersalClockTree
extends Object
    For a given clock region Y coordinate domain range (e.g. Y1-Y5), provides a set of clock root options with corresponding vertical distribution paths for each target clock region.

        public List<Pair<IntentCode,ClockRegion>> getClockRegionVDistrPath(ClockRegion target)
        Gets the vertical distribution path of the target clock region for the preferred clock root.
        Parameters:
        target - The destination clock region that needs to be routed via vertical distribution lines.
        Returns:
